{"article_id":"htioZYlidjsHCw9C","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The American Bar Association","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"- the legal profession ' s largest group -","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"is urging the Senate Judiciary Committee to postpone Friday ' s initial vote on Brett Kavanaugh","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"until an FBI probe is conducted on the sexual assault allegations","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"facing the Supreme Court nominee .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"\" The basic principles","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"that underscore the Senate ' s constitutional duty of advice and consent on federal judicial nominees","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"require nothing less than a careful examination of the accusations and facts by the FBI , \"","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"ABA president Robert Carlson wrote late Thursday to Chairman Chuck Grassley","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"( R-Iowa )","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"and ranking Democrat Dianne Feinstein of California ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"according to the Washington Post .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"\" Each appointment to our nation ' s Highest Court","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"( as with all others )","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"is simply too important","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"to rush to a vote , \"","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Carlson wrote .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"\" Deciding to proceed","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"without conducting an additional investigation","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"would not only have a lasting impact on the Senate ' s reputation ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"but it will also negatively affect the great trust","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"necessary for the American people to have in the Supreme Court . \"","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"As he vigorously denied allegations by Christine Blasey Ford","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"that he sexually assaulted her","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"when they were teens ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Kavanaugh touted his \" well-qualified \" rating by the ABA for the Supreme Court ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"he was \" thoroughly vetted \" by the 400,000-member group .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"\" For 12 years , everyone","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"who has appeared before me on the DC Circuit","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"has praised my judicial temperament , \"","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Kavanaugh said Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"\" That ' s why I have the unanimous , well-qualified rating from the American Bar Association . \"","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Republican Sen. Lindsey Graham ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"who angrily blasted the Democrats ' handling of the nomination process ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"has described the ABA ' s unanimous favorable rating as the \" gold standard . \"","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"As part of its review of the judge ' s qualifications , the ABA ' s Standing Committee on the Federal Judiciary found","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"that Kavanaugh \" enjoys an excellent reputation for integrity","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"and is a person of outstanding character . \"","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"see also","depth":3},{"id":40,"text":"Senate panel says","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"it will vote Friday on Kavanaugh nomination","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"The Senate Judiciary Committee said Thursday night","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"that it plans ...","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"The Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"- with 11 Republicans and 10 Democrats -","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"announced late Thursday","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that it will meet at 9:30 a.m. Friday","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"to vote on Kavanaugh ' s nomination ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"with a final confirmation vote expected Tuesday .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"After the hearing , Republicans met in private","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"to discuss the next steps .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Four senators","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"who have not taken firm positions on the nominee","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"met separately after the hearing .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"The four","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"- Republicans Jeff Flake of Arizona , Susan Collins of Maine and Lisa Murkowski of Alaska and Democrat Joe Manchin of West Virginia -","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"are seen as swing votes","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"who could decide the outcome of the closely contested nomination .","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"If all 10 Democrats vote against Kavanaugh ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"the spotlight would shine on Flake ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"who is retiring after this year","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"and has shown a willingness","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"to defy President Trump .","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"In calling for the FBI probe","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"before any vote happens ,","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"Carlson urged the Senate to \" remain an institution","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"that will reliably follow the law and not politics . \"","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"Related Video","depth":3},{"id":69,"text":"Video length 1 minute 36 seconds 1:36","depth":3},{"id":70,"text":"Ford wanted two front doors in her home ,","depth":4},{"id":71,"text":"and says","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"it 's all because of Kavanaugh","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"Ford wanted two front doors in her home ,","depth":4},{"id":74,"text":"and says","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"it 's all because of Kavanaugh","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":151,"left":143,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":114,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":97,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":80,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":78,"right":79,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":77,"right":2,"relatio